                        <p style="line-height: 1.5 !important; margin: 0;">With its focus on innovation and impact, <a href="https://foundation.uc.edu/campaign/about" style="color: var(--color-brand-black);"><strong><em>Next, <span style="color: #e00122; font-weight: inherit;">Now</span>: The Campaign for Cincinnati</em></strong></a> is where ambition meets action. At the University of Cincinnati and UC Health, we’re driven by next; thinking bolder and dreaming bigger to create the tomorrow we envision, today.<br><br>What’s <strong><em>NEXT</em></strong>, starts with you.</p>
